  "hashtags" : [ ],
  "sections" : [ {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 1",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "When we walk with the Lord",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 22
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "In the light of His word;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "What a glory He sheds on our way,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 16
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 29
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "While we do His good will,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 21
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "He abides with us still,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 4
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 18
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And with all who will trust and obey.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 22
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "chorus",
    "label" : "CHORUS",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Trust and obey, for there's no other way,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 0
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 11
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 28
      }, {
        "chord" : "B",
        "position" : 37
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "To be happy in Jesus but to trust and obey.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "E",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 15
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 28
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 34
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 39
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 2",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Not a shadow can rise",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 17
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Not a cloud in the skies,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "But His smile quickly drives it away;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 22
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Not a doubt not a fear,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 18
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Not a sigh nor a tear,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 17
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Can abide while we trust and obey.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 5
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 19
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 30
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 3",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Not a burden we bear,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 16
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Not a sorrow we share,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 16
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "But our toil He doth richly repay,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 21
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 30
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Not a grief nor a loss,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 18
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Not a frown not a cross,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 18
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "But is blest if we trust and obey.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 19
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 30
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 4",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "But we never can prove,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 7
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 17
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "The delights of His love,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 20
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Until all on the altar we lay,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 2
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 17
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 26
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "For the favor He shows,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 17
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "And the joy He bestows,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 17
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Are for them who will trust and obey.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 22
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    } ]
  }, {
    "type" : "verse",
    "label" : "VERSE 5",
    "lines" : [ {
      "text" : "Then in fellowship sweet;",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "We will sit at His feet,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 19
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Or we'll walk by His side in the way,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 21
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 33
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "What He says we will do,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 8
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 21
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Where He sends we will go,",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 9
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 23
      } ]
    }, {
      "text" : "Never fear, only trust and obey.",
      "chords" : [ {
        "chord" : "G",
        "position" : 6
      }, {
        "chord" : "A",
        "position" : 17
      }, {
        "chord" : "D",
        "position" : 28
      } ]
    } ]
  } ]
}